issue.title: Adding more CLI Flags
issue.body:
First off, I think this tool is great, but I wanted to leave feedback that I think could make it an even better tool so that I, or someone else, could pick the ideas up at a later date.

After messing around with it to generate RESTCONF documentation, these are the flags I wish it had:

`-api-version <string> (default: "1.0")`

Currently, when using the CLI, the version number has to be manually added in order to convert to OpenAPI 3.0.

`-format <enum> (default: yaml) (options: json, yaml)`

Some other tools that digest swagger prefer JSON.

`-version`

See what version of yang2swagger is running.
